channel.title: Black Screen Of Death?
channel.description:
Whenever I log in to a MoparScape server on the web client, EVERY SINGLE TIME, this happens: [img]http://hyfer.wikispaces.com/file/view/server_1.png/190668730/server_1.png[/img]
And on the odd time that something DOES work, the screen is black like this: [img]http://i868.photobucket.com/albums/ab246/triplehhhhhh/NewBitmapImage15-1.jpg[/img]
I have looked all around the internet trying to find out how to fix this. NOTHING has worked. PLEASE, tell me ANYTHING you know that might fix this.
kthxbai.
